  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6558564/" class="title-link">止战之殇——读山冈庄八的《太平洋战争》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6558564"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/14489661/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u14489661-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/14489661/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">九歌无题</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-02-22"
      class="main-meta">2014-02-22 21:25:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6558564_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         关于太平洋战争的书读得不是太多，以往只是通过各种资料拼贴起一个大概轮廓。在网上偶然看到有关介绍，意识到对太平洋战争有些印象模糊，产生了再行了解的想法。拿到书后觉的与传统历史书籍和畅销写史书籍不太一样，意识到这是本小说，而真正去读的时候，发现它的确是一...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6558564_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6558564_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7531325">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7531325/" class="title-link">关于日本人的历史观</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7531325"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sl19910727/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51551898-10.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sl19910727/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">霜月落</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-07-13"
      class="main-meta">2015-07-13 21:25:34</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7531325_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    《太平洋战争》这本书连载于20世纪60年代，恰好是日本战后走上复兴的历史时期，彼时参加或亲历过二战的日本民众正值中壮年，而生于战后的一代人未及弱冠，可以说这本小说是反映那一代人“三观”的集中体现。通过字里行间，我们可以窥得日本民众，尤其是政治高层与右翼份子的...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7531325_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7531325_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5394742">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5394742/" class="title-link">值得一看的历史战争小说</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5394742"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/defeisituo/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u44657881-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/defeisituo/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">defeisituo</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-04-18"
      class="main-meta">2012-04-18 22:31:51</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5394742_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  日本人很决绝，很武士道精神。大和民族真是一个奇怪的民族，在战争中尤其显得明显。比如《菊与刀》是战后的一本非常著名的人类学考察报告，说明透过战争，也只有在战争中才能对日本民族认识的更加清楚。    觉得山冈庄八的文笔确实平静中带着洒脱或者一丝丝悲凉的幽默！

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5394742_full" class="hidden">
